{"tid":444133,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺少左好多人打籃球","createTime":"2017-10-22T08:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T13:10:48.000Z","uid":54581,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1e7814257fc22ccbc6716b29a235afc3254001c0","tid":444133,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:46:20.000Z","msg":"以前中學 放學時間去親邊個場都係咁撚多人<br />\n<br />\n近排屎忽痕想打波，發現屋企附近幾個場都係空既，不論閒日平日 放學夜晚都係咁<br />\n<br />\n明明附近都有屋苑有學校，唔明why會無人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da85643be658da9407a831bd3b754746c79ddd7","tid":444133,"uid":54025,"like":11,"dislike":9,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:49:22.000Z","msg":"玩具少人玩正常<br />\n<br />\n依家玩iphone"},{"pid":"3c282e9d8f7f74e8759fce06610b1f5d4ba98b78","tid":444133,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:51:22.000Z","msg":"正常，以為大隻打開波嗰d<br />\n通常都頭腦簡單<br />\n<br />\n好多去晒做健身公司，跑數，呃人<br />\n仲衰過倫敦金"},{"pid":"e62141e844a153136ccbd25857e8045929fb3572","tid":444133,"uid":54581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩具少人玩正常<br />\n<br />\n依家玩iphone</blockquote><br />\n依家個代掛住打機同打飛機 <br />\n又唔打波<br />\n<br />\n平均都咁高，公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16c385b38cc37a456830cca5572f0020f8e9f08","tid":444133,"uid":82915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:53:04.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"1850c3081632e4429162b482198649d31be04423","tid":444133,"uid":32132,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:09:29.000Z","msg":"玩玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不了"},{"pid":"36477230e35bfbc272916ca861dd5208351682e6","tid":444133,"uid":5077,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:24:36.000Z","msg":"開始轉涼，怕凍親"},{"pid":"870eab3a6e3861933a626eab8cda5c3cf8679cb2","tid":444133,"uid":29093,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:27:20.000Z","msg":"全部溝哂女上哂岸啦<br />\n<br />\n邊似班足波撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   成身臭汗去迫茶記"},{"pid":"7c5eaef30bd65acc5e4d5a30a1e1188ca67b8bf8","tid":444133,"uid":104026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:36:54.000Z","msg":"呢家啲學生個個溫書補習，邊有時間玩玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d745cdfa23a309d238bde77b8d0f2c576693955f","tid":444133,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開始轉涼，怕凍親</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa02834f458c49f1b0fd7094ea98c9d58fa9335","tid":444133,"uid":7371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"其實我細個時好少人打籃球<br />\n個時街場得一兩個人射下波多<br />\n自從Slam Dunk出後<br />\n突然多左好多人跟風打籃球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個當自己係流川楓或三井壽<br />\n配合當時亞視播NBA地帶先多左人睇NBA<br />\n<br />\n近年冇乜籃球動漫hit得起<br />\n所以好難比到人打籃球個種熱血感覺<br />\n<br />\n好多當年迷Slam Dunk嘅人可能玩緊NBA 2K<br />\nNBA 2K好擬真好過自己打波啦<br />\n個批人個個三十幾四十歲<br />\n返工或有家室<br />\n約齊人打波都難"},{"pid":"d6e5a9657a452f92e12f9a885bfa8cdd65235ecd","tid":444133,"uid":13260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T10:26:53.000Z","msg":"玩具始終有過氣既一日"},{"pid":"da94c1cfd9a707dfcac893cfbd103d3f17fac429","tid":444133,"uid":145610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T10:35:42.000Z","msg":"唔覺，早前想打，唔係book左場就排6-7隊<br />\n好啦轉去另一個場打，又係咁<br />\n最後放棄番屋企，無再打過籃球<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151bc2e08eb2664e122f7d95ae684befa2fa197a","tid":444133,"uid":97626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔覺，早前想打，唔係book左場就排6-7隊<br />\n好啦轉去另一個場打，又係咁<br />\n最後放棄番屋企，無再打過籃球<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個啲係最大既場 <br />\n<br />\n細場係吉"},{"pid":"0aab3b855e7c3b8e74f9873e2c1c511f22ee2c71","tid":444133,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"去晒大場"},{"pid":"97000e01383fcca4f8e936af447a033cc33c5000","tid":444133,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"玩具有人玩架咩???<br />\n利申玩玩具"},{"pid":"2faa6afbfc6b3773076c2d1e622d59668445db9d","tid":444133,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去晒大場</blockquote><br />\n打波都要出灣仔旺角，屌那星"},{"pid":"1c2e5725aca10a816820d4ddf361fdb9ef5db624","tid":444133,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"去晒LOL <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053a4e47f04498f17123ed312eb2a68a22751764","tid":444133,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"玩具反斗城都破產啦<br />\n藍波冇人玩都正常😂😂😂"},{"pid":"1c8d76478ef798fc3541053a17251263ab43b24f","tid":444133,"uid":117909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"吊而家真係少左好多人"},{"pid":"12e1ab86642c2db090a497e11c5e3b1d41fd77b2","tid":444133,"uid":94551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T15:01:01.000Z","msg":"足撚有幾多個落場踢呀<br />\n收皮啦"},{"pid":"21000f87f8b7f35c1f2e0f8ce62ef569bb037945","tid":444133,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T15:04:23.000Z","msg":"真係忍唔撚住屌鳩你，無人打咪仲好啦，自己練吓波唔得嘅，要人同你打，返去揾你老母打啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf23d7da3ff815b82685975e5a1211a4363ac1e","tid":444133,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係忍唔撚住屌鳩你，無人打咪仲好啦，自己練吓波唔得嘅，要人同你打，返去揾你老母打啦！<img s